Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢？松川選手該怎麼進攻才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，要是我的話肯定會投較低的直線球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先投個較高的壞球作為迷惑球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之較高的好球…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，松川投了一個上升曲線球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中了！球向中野飛去，越飛越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中區看台！中區看台！掉進去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田！擊出了激動人心的本壘打！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要到這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡，我念的中學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有我的許多回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去上學，一起學習，一起養花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一個比他大12歲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊，原來我那麼輕易的就被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然開始了，就不能半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此你才來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液的顏色發生了變化，大家都變得不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有人覺得這很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕啊！ 綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon的自主意識活動超出了預想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三輪副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏者出了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快通知九鬼一佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把這件事報告給麻彌大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦暫時處於電荷異常狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止Xephon的自主意識活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼可擔心不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就是個好孩子，這一點我最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是由我親手撫養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名綾人…真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你要相信自己就是綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是其他的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是為你而存在的，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為你一個人而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你為了成為真的奏者去了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此這個世界發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不必再去配合你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是迷戀著他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惑之森，覺醒之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的歎息，只放出銀色的光輝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是鳥飼君你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來綾人家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她與此事無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九鬼，伊修特利出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動Allegretto和Falsetto去鎮壓Xephon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.47,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Falsetto：意大利語，聲樂術語，假聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院方面也要派人去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可疑女子，最好調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，Falsetto
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微平靜一些了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被TERRA稱為MU族的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕大部分的都沒能到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘救生船到達這裡的只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在，他們還是那種不與Dolem同步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法生存下去的藍色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，MU族也是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是MU族？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說的在我小的時候就去世的父親也是的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你穿上你平時的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做MU族領導者時穿的服裝，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼，你到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在欺騙我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣，就輕鬆多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等…不要！不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，你真的是我的母親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以，我會很願意生下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(MU族語)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，很順利，這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allegretto到底在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，是TERRA的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六道翔吾的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是遙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你動，我就開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得勇敢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名？神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色的吧？是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的，是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，我已經不能再留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話，我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
